OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 13 MAY
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1985FThe first edition of Connections
OL,7,Fairs on ITV.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1990FTransmission of the 9.05pm BBC
OL,10,FNews (BBC One) with Michael Buerk was
OL,11,Fhalted at 9.17pm due to a power cut,
OL,12,Fwhich affected BBC Television Centre
OL,13,Fand part of London W12. The bulletin
OL,14,Fresumed at 10pm, with poor studio
OL,15,Flighting, after That's Life. Michael
OL,16,FBuerk apologised for the interruption.
OL,17,
OL,18,CG2007FThe first episode of Gavin and
OL,19,FStacey airs on BBC Three. Written by
OL,20,Fand starring James Corden and Ruth
OL,21,FJones.
OL,22,
